{
  "stem": "23506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we sit in the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is the most dangerous place where you can sit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They announced that the train is going to leave at 4:30 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 4:30 in the morning-- and where are we going to go?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have where to-- you cannot stay in the train station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I saw a group of Polish people coming from the train from Radom and I saw a railroad engineer-- he looked to me-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have the intuition that this would be the right person to go ask.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went over to him and I ask him-- with my brother-- do you, do you know where there is a place that we can stay overnight?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we looked at all those, those renting houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On that street, there were very more places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But for me and my brother to stay, I would be gladly staying there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they didn't have a place for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this man looked at me and looked at my brother and said, did you come from that train?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I, I lied to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I will let-- I will-- you can stay in my house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took us at night to his place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we pretended that, that we don't know that it's not-- we don't know the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he let us sit in his kitchen on the coal something-- box.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, I will wake you up at four-- 4:00, so you will have time to go to the station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- when the time came, he came in the, in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was already dressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sitting with my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
